{
  "slug": "death-penalty",
  "split_strategy": "sentence_or_phrase",
  "phrase_chars": 42,
  "caption_count": 90,
  "max_caption_chars": 42,
  "duration": 546.624,
  "items": [
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "正方主張：我國應廢除死刑，改以終身監禁、不得假釋或極嚴格假釋審查、",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0001.mp3",
      "duration": 7.2,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 7.2
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "被害人支持制度與司法防錯機制，作為處理最嚴重犯罪的制度核心。",
      "char_count": 30,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0002.mp3",
      "duration": 6.024,
      "start": 7.2,
      "end": 13.224
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "第一，死刑的不可逆性使司法錯誤無法補救。",
      "char_count": 20,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0003.mp3",
      "duration": 4.464,
      "start": 13.224,
      "end": 17.688000000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "刑事司法再嚴謹，仍可能受到偵查偏誤、證據污染、鑑定錯誤、辯護資源不均與社會輿論影響。",
      "char_count": 42,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0004.mp3",
      "duration": 8.856,
      "start": 17.688000000000002,
      "end": 26.544000000000004
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "一般刑罰若判錯，至少仍有釋放、補償與名譽回復的空間；死刑一旦執行，",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0005.mp3",
      "duration": 6.984,
      "start": 26.544000000000004,
      "end": 33.528000000000006
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "國家就沒有修正錯誤的能力。",
      "char_count": 13,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0006.mp3",
      "duration": 3.192,
      "start": 33.528000000000006,
      "end": 36.720000000000006
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "第二，死刑無法證明是不可替代的嚇阻工具。",
      "char_count": 20,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0007.mp3",
      "duration": 4.536,
      "start": 36.720000000000006,
      "end": 41.25600000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "主張保留死刑者常說它可以預防重大犯罪，但重大暴力犯罪多發生在衝動、精神失衡、",
      "char_count": 38,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0008.mp3",
      "duration": 7.824,
      "start": 41.25600000000001,
      "end": 49.080000000000005
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "親密關係崩解、組織犯罪或極端絕望情境中，行為人未必會理性計算刑度。",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0009.mp3",
      "duration": 6.816,
      "start": 49.080000000000005,
      "end": 55.89600000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "真正能降低犯罪的是警政效率、社會安全網、精神醫療、家暴防治、槍械與刀械管制、",
      "char_count": 38,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0010.mp3",
      "duration": 8.28,
      "start": 55.89600000000001,
      "end": 64.176
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "再犯風險管理，而不是把刑罰推到最終極。",
      "char_count": 19,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0011.mp3",
      "duration": 4.584,
      "start": 64.176,
      "end": 68.76
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "第三，國家不能用不可逆的殺人來宣示正義。",
      "char_count": 20,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0012.mp3",
      "duration": 4.368,
      "start": 68.76,
      "end": 73.128
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "刑罰的目的應是保護社會、回應被害、矯正可能矯正者，並維持法治秩序。",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0013.mp3",
      "duration": 7.176,
      "start": 73.128,
      "end": 80.304
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "死刑看似給出最強烈的譴責，卻也讓國家把人的生命排除在制度修復之外。",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0014.mp3",
      "duration": 6.504,
      "start": 80.304,
      "end": 86.808
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "當憲法法庭已強調生命權受最高程度保障時，廢死不是縱容犯罪，而是要求國家用更成熟、",
      "char_count": 40,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0015.mp3",
      "duration": 8.28,
      "start": 86.808,
      "end": 95.08800000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "更不會犯下終局錯誤的方式處理極惡案件。",
      "char_count": 19,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0016.mp3",
      "duration": 4.128,
      "start": 95.08800000000001,
      "end": 99.21600000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "正方定義的「廢除」不是放任重罪犯回到社會，而是取消國家執行死刑的權力，",
      "char_count": 35,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0017.mp3",
      "duration": 6.768,
      "start": 99.21600000000001,
      "end": 105.98400000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "並同步建立三項配套：一是重大殺人案件可處終身監禁或長期隔離；",
      "char_count": 30,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0018.mp3",
      "duration": 6.264,
      "start": 105.98400000000001,
      "end": 112.248
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "二是強化被害人與家屬的資訊、心理、經濟與訴訟支持；",
      "char_count": 25,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0019.mp3",
      "duration": 5.808,
      "start": 112.248,
      "end": 118.05600000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "正方申論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "三是建立嚴格的冤案複查與量刑審查制度。",
      "char_count": 19,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0020.mp3",
      "duration": 4.2,
      "start": 118.05600000000001,
      "end": 122.25600000000001
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "反方主張：我國目前不應廢除死刑，而應保留極少數、最嚴格條件下適用的死刑制度。",
      "char_count": 38,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0021.mp3",
      "duration": 8.232,
      "start": 122.25600000000001,
      "end": 130.488
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "理由不是崇尚報復，而是面對最嚴重犯罪時，國家仍需要最後手段來維持正義、",
      "char_count": 35,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0022.mp3",
      "duration": 7.68,
      "start": 130.488,
      "end": 138.168
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "安定與人民對司法的信任。",
      "char_count": 12,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0023.mp3",
      "duration": 3.024,
      "start": 138.168,
      "end": 141.192
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "第一，死刑具有極端案件中的應報正義功能。",
      "char_count": 20,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0024.mp3",
      "duration": 4.56,
      "start": 141.192,
      "end": 145.752
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "某些案件不只是造成死亡，而是包含凌虐、隨機殺人、連續殺人、",
      "char_count": 29,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0025.mp3",
      "duration": 7.056,
      "start": 145.752,
      "end": 152.80800000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "殺害兒童或對社會安全造成巨大破壞。",
      "char_count": 17,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0026.mp3",
      "duration": 4.2,
      "start": 152.80800000000002,
      "end": 157.008
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "若刑罰完全排除死刑，社會可能認為國家對最嚴重侵害生命的行為沒有相稱回應。",
      "char_count": 36,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0027.mp3",
      "duration": 7.68,
      "start": 157.008,
      "end": 164.68800000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "刑罰若失去相稱性，人民可能轉向私刑情緒，反而傷害法治。",
      "char_count": 27,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0028.mp3",
      "duration": 6.408,
      "start": 164.68800000000002,
      "end": 171.096
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "第二，死刑仍有隔離與象徵性嚇阻功能。",
      "char_count": 18,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0029.mp3",
      "duration": 4.416,
      "start": 171.096,
      "end": 175.512
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "雖然死刑的嚇阻效果難以用單一數據證明，但不能反過來說它完全沒有作用。",
      "char_count": 34,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0030.mp3",
      "duration": 7.08,
      "start": 175.512,
      "end": 182.592
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "刑罰制度本來就包含一般預防、特別預防與價值宣示。",
      "char_count": 24,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0031.mp3",
      "duration": 5.496,
      "start": 182.592,
      "end": 188.08800000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "對蓄意計畫、組織性或恐怖性犯罪而言，最嚴重刑罰仍可能是行為人風險評估的一部分。",
      "char_count": 39,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0032.mp3",
      "duration": 8.376,
      "start": 188.08800000000002,
      "end": 196.46400000000003
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "第三，台灣憲法法庭並未宣告死刑違憲，而是要求更高門檻。",
      "char_count": 27,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0033.mp3",
      "duration": 6.408,
      "start": 196.46400000000003,
      "end": 202.872
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "這給出的方向不是立即廢除，而是限縮、審慎、程序強化。",
      "char_count": 26,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0034.mp3",
      "duration": 6.312,
      "start": 202.872,
      "end": 209.18400000000003
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "也就是說，現階段最合憲、最符合民意與制度穩定的做法，",
      "char_count": 26,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0035.mp3",
      "duration": 6.0,
      "start": 209.18400000000003,
      "end": 215.18400000000003
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "是保留死刑但讓它只存在於極端例外中。",
      "char_count": 18,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0036.mp3",
      "duration": 4.248,
      "start": 215.18400000000003,
      "end": 219.43200000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "反方承認冤案風險與程序保障的重要性，因此主張改革而非廢除：死刑案件必須有強制辯護、",
      "char_count": 41,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0037.mp3",
      "duration": 8.928,
      "start": 219.43200000000002,
      "end": 228.36
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "言詞辯論、最嚴格證據法則、精神鑑定、量刑理由審查與非常救濟機制。",
      "char_count": 32,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0038.mp3",
      "duration": 7.608,
      "start": 228.36,
      "end": 235.96800000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "反方申論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "若程序不可靠，就不應判死；但若程序已達最高標準，仍應保留最後刑罰。",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0039.mp3",
      "duration": 7.44,
      "start": 235.96800000000002,
      "end": 243.40800000000002
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "反方的核心問題在於：它承認死刑有不可逆風險，卻仍要求國家保留不可逆權力。",
      "char_count": 36,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0040.mp3",
      "duration": 7.152,
      "start": 243.40800000000002,
      "end": 250.56
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "這裡存在制度矛盾。",
      "char_count": 9,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0041.mp3",
      "duration": 2.808,
      "start": 250.56,
      "end": 253.368
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "若我們真的相信司法可能出錯，合理回應應是移除無法補救的刑罰，",
      "char_count": 30,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0042.mp3",
      "duration": 6.0,
      "start": 253.368,
      "end": 259.368
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "而不是說「只要更小心就好」。",
      "char_count": 14,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0043.mp3",
      "duration": 3.528,
      "start": 259.368,
      "end": 262.896
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "因為死刑錯誤的成本不是金錢、時間或程序重開，而是一個人被國家永久消滅。",
      "char_count": 35,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0044.mp3",
      "duration": 7.104,
      "start": 262.896,
      "end": 270.0
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "反方說死刑維持相稱性，但相稱性不等於必須以命償命。",
      "char_count": 25,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0045.mp3",
      "duration": 5.544,
      "start": 270.0,
      "end": 275.544
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "現代刑罰可以用終身監禁、長期隔離、不得假釋或嚴格假釋審查，表達對重罪的最強譴責。",
      "char_count": 40,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0046.mp3",
      "duration": 8.376,
      "start": 275.544,
      "end": 283.91999999999996
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "真正的問題不是刑罰夠不夠重，而是制度能不能同時保護社會、避免冤錯、照顧被害人。",
      "char_count": 39,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0047.mp3",
      "duration": 7.872,
      "start": 283.91999999999996,
      "end": 291.792
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "把死刑當作正義的象徵，容易讓社會誤以為「槍決」就是結案，",
      "char_count": 28,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0048.mp3",
      "duration": 5.544,
      "start": 291.792,
      "end": 297.33599999999996
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "反而忽略被害家庭長期支持與犯罪預防。",
      "char_count": 18,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0049.mp3",
      "duration": 4.176,
      "start": 297.33599999999996,
      "end": 301.51199999999994
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "反方也沒有證明死刑的嚇阻效果優於替代制度。",
      "char_count": 21,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0050.mp3",
      "duration": 4.608,
      "start": 301.51199999999994,
      "end": 306.11999999999995
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "若一項刑罰不可逆、可能錯殺、對嚇阻效果又沒有穩定證明，國家就不應繼續依賴它。",
      "char_count": 38,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0051.mp3",
      "duration": 7.368,
      "start": 306.11999999999995,
      "end": 313.48799999999994
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "憲法法庭雖未宣告死刑全面違憲，但判決已大幅提高死刑適用門檻，",
      "char_count": 30,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0052.mp3",
      "duration": 6.288,
      "start": 313.48799999999994,
      "end": 319.77599999999995
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "並強調生命權受最高程度保障。",
      "char_count": 14,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0053.mp3",
      "duration": 3.528,
      "start": 319.77599999999995,
      "end": 323.304
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "正方的主張正是沿著這個方向往前走：把例外縮到制度上不再需要，最後以可補救、可審查、",
      "char_count": 41,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0054.mp3",
      "duration": 8.064,
      "start": 323.304,
      "end": 331.368
    },
    {
      "section": "正方駁論",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "可持續的刑罰取代死刑。",
      "char_count": 11,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0055.mp3",
      "duration": 3.096,
      "start": 331.368,
      "end": 334.464
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "正方把「可能錯判」推論成「必須廢除」，但這個推論過度跳躍。",
      "char_count": 29,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0056.mp3",
      "duration": 6.408,
      "start": 334.464,
      "end": 340.872
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "任何刑罰都可能因錯判造成巨大傷害，包括長期監禁也可能毀掉一個人的人生。",
      "char_count": 35,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0057.mp3",
      "duration": 7.344,
      "start": 340.872,
      "end": 348.216
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "制度面對風險的方式，通常是提高證明標準、改善辯護品質、建立救濟程序，",
      "char_count": 34,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0058.mp3",
      "duration": 7.752,
      "start": 348.216,
      "end": 355.968
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "而不是取消最重刑罰。",
      "char_count": 10,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0059.mp3",
      "duration": 2.784,
      "start": 355.968,
      "end": 358.752
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "若因可能錯判就廢除死刑，那同樣邏輯也會動搖無期徒刑與長期自由刑。",
      "char_count": 32,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0060.mp3",
      "duration": 7.224,
      "start": 358.752,
      "end": 365.976
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "正方說終身監禁可以替代死刑，但沒有處理兩個問題。",
      "char_count": 24,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0061.mp3",
      "duration": 5.52,
      "start": 365.976,
      "end": 371.496
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "第一，若終身監禁未來仍有假釋或政治性減刑可能，社會對極端重罪的安全疑慮仍會存在。",
      "char_count": 40,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0062.mp3",
      "duration": 8.496,
      "start": 371.496,
      "end": 379.99199999999996
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "第二，長期監禁本身也可能被批評為慢性折磨，並不必然比死刑更人道。",
      "char_count": 32,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0063.mp3",
      "duration": 7.104,
      "start": 379.99199999999996,
      "end": 387.09599999999995
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "正方需要提出非常具體、可被社會信任的替代制度，而不只是說「終身隔離」。",
      "char_count": 35,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0064.mp3",
      "duration": 7.488,
      "start": 387.09599999999995,
      "end": 394.58399999999995
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "正方也低估民意與司法信任。",
      "char_count": 13,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0065.mp3",
      "duration": 3.36,
      "start": 394.58399999999995,
      "end": 397.94399999999996
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "刑罰制度不能完全由民意決定，但也不能完全無視人民對生命安全與公平報應的期待。",
      "char_count": 38,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0066.mp3",
      "duration": 7.776,
      "start": 397.94399999999996,
      "end": 405.71999999999997
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "對被害人家屬而言，廢除死刑若沒有足夠配套，可能被理解成國家優先保護加害人。",
      "char_count": 37,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0067.mp3",
      "duration": 8.04,
      "start": 405.71999999999997,
      "end": 413.76
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "現階段較穩健的改革路線，是把死刑限縮到最嚴重、證據最明確、程序最嚴格的案件，",
      "char_count": 38,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0068.mp3",
      "duration": 8.544,
      "start": 413.76,
      "end": 422.304
    },
    {
      "section": "反方駁論",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "而不是直接廢除。",
      "char_count": 8,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0069.mp3",
      "duration": 2.328,
      "start": 422.304,
      "end": 424.63199999999995
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "反方最後強調：不應廢除死刑，不代表濫用死刑。",
      "char_count": 22,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0070.mp3",
      "duration": 5.256,
      "start": 424.63199999999995,
      "end": 429.8879999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "反方支持的是極端例外、嚴格審查、程序完備的保留死刑制度。",
      "char_count": 28,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0071.mp3",
      "duration": 6.312,
      "start": 429.8879999999999,
      "end": 436.19999999999993
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "正方最大的矛盾，是一方面承認有極端惡性犯罪需要長期隔離，",
      "char_count": 28,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0072.mp3",
      "duration": 6.024,
      "start": 436.19999999999993,
      "end": 442.22399999999993
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "另一方面卻否認社會可以保留最嚴重刑罰作為最後界線。",
      "char_count": 25,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0073.mp3",
      "duration": 5.688,
      "start": 442.22399999999993,
      "end": 447.9119999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "若國家完全取消死刑，面對最殘酷、最不可挽回的殺人案件時，",
      "char_count": 28,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0074.mp3",
      "duration": 6.456,
      "start": 447.9119999999999,
      "end": 454.36799999999994
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "司法可能被認為失去最終回應能力。",
      "char_count": 16,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0075.mp3",
      "duration": 3.96,
      "start": 454.36799999999994,
      "end": 458.3279999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "我國憲法法庭的方向不是立刻廢死，而是要求死刑必須更加慎重。",
      "char_count": 29,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0076.mp3",
      "duration": 6.336,
      "start": 458.3279999999999,
      "end": 464.66399999999993
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "這正符合反方立場：改革程序、限縮適用、避免冤案，但仍保留最後手段。",
      "char_count": 33,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0077.mp3",
      "duration": 7.68,
      "start": 464.66399999999993,
      "end": 472.34399999999994
    },
    {
      "section": "反方結辯",
      "speaker": "反方 Gemini",
      "voice": "zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural",
      "rate": "+3%",
      "pitch": "+2Hz",
      "text": "對於被害人、社會安全與法治信任而言，現階段不應倉促廢除死刑。",
      "char_count": 30,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0078.mp3",
      "duration": 6.864,
      "start": 472.34399999999994,
      "end": 479.2079999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "正方最後要指出：反方說保留死刑是「最後手段」，但沒有回答最根本問題：",
      "char_count": 34,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0079.mp3",
      "duration": 6.744,
      "start": 479.2079999999999,
      "end": 485.9519999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "如果最後手段錯了，誰來補救？",
      "char_count": 14,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0080.mp3",
      "duration": 3.576,
      "start": 485.9519999999999,
      "end": 489.5279999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "一個制度只要仍允許不可逆錯誤，就不能只靠「我們會更小心」來取得正當性。",
      "char_count": 35,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0081.mp3",
      "duration": 6.384,
      "start": 489.5279999999999,
      "end": 495.9119999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "廢除死刑不是否定被害人的痛，也不是替加害人開脫。",
      "char_count": 24,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0082.mp3",
      "duration": 5.112,
      "start": 495.9119999999999,
      "end": 501.02399999999994
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "相反地，廢死要求國家把資源放在真正能保護人的地方：更可靠的偵查審判、",
      "char_count": 34,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0083.mp3",
      "duration": 6.984,
      "start": 501.02399999999994,
      "end": 508.0079999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "更長期的被害人支持、更有效的犯罪預防、更嚴格的重罪隔離制度。",
      "char_count": 30,
      "file": "debates/death-penalty/podcast/caption-segments/0084.mp3",
      "duration": 6.36,
      "start": 508.0079999999999,
      "end": 514.3679999999999
    },
    {
      "section": "正方結辯",
      "speaker": "正方 Claude",
      "voice": "zh-TW-YunJheNeural",
      "rate": "-1%",
      "pitch": "-1Hz",
      "text": "死刑提供的是終局感，但不一定提供真正的安全。",
      "char_count": 22,
